%%{init: {'flowchart': {'curve': 'stepAfter', 'nodeSpacing': 30, 'rankSpacing': 40}}}%%
flowchart LR
    classDef startEnd fill:#000,stroke:#000,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#FFD700,stroke:#B8860B,color:#000
    classDef activity fill:#fff,stroke:#000,color:#000

    Start((Start)):::startEnd

    Start --> UserValid[User<br/>Validation]:::activity
    UserValid --> AuthCheck{Login<br/>Failed}:::decision
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| ForgotPW[Forgot Password]:::activity
    ForgotPW --> ResetPW[Reset<br/>Password]:::activity
    ResetPW --> UserValid
    AuthCheck -->|No| Dashboard[Display Exclusive<br/>SOC Dashboard]:::activity
    Dashboard --> D1{Action?}:::decision

    D1 -->|Logout| Logout[Log out]:::activity
    Logout --> EndL((End)):::startEnd

    D1 -->|View Team| ViewTeam[View Team<br/>Members &<br/>Roles]:::activity
    ViewTeam --> MA{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    D1 -->|DurianBot AI| AskQ[Type Open-Ended<br/>Threat Analysis<br/>Question]:::activity
    AskQ --> CallOllama[Call Ollama LLM<br/>with Alert Context]:::activity
    CallOllama --> DisplayAI[Display AI<br/>Threat Analysis<br/>Response]:::activity
    DisplayAI --> ContinueQ{Continue<br/>chat?}:::decision
    ContinueQ -->|Yes| AskQ
    ContinueQ -->|No| MB{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    D1 -->|Attack Chains| ViewChains[View Attack<br/>Chain Timeline]:::activity
    ViewChains --> ChainDetail[View Kill Chain<br/>Visualisation &<br/>MITRE Phases]:::activity
    ChainDetail --> MC{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    D1 -->|Risk Scores| ViewRisk[View Dynamic<br/>Risk Score]:::activity
    ViewRisk --> RiskBreakdown[View Risk Factor<br/>Breakdown<br/>0 - 100]:::activity
    RiskBreakdown --> MD{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    MA -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MB -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MC -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MD -->|Yes| Dashboard

    MA -->|No| E1((End)):::startEnd
    MB -->|No| E2((End)):::startEnd
    MC -->|No| E3((End)):::startEnd
    MD -->|No| E4((End)):::startEnd
